properties.Observation: Cattles have access into the brook. The right bank is eroded and the vegetation is detroyed. The water is brownish due to the sedimentation. Heavy sedimentation in the stream.

Wood debris jam. There is sediment accumulation in the stream and in the debris jam. Little erosion on both sides of the bank.
